    <text>
        <body>
            
            <div1 type="letter">
                
                <pb facs="nei.j4c.20.80" />
                <fw type="curatorial">80</fw>
                
                <note type="curatorial">
                    WESTERN HISTORICAL MANUSCRIPTS COLLECTION<lb/>
                    UNIVERSITY OF MISSOURI<lb/>
                    COLUMBIA, MO.
                </note>
                
                <fw type="letterhead">
                <hi rend="caps">SKYRIM FARM</hi>
                <lb/>
                <hi rend="caps">ROUTE 7</hi>
                <lb/>
                <hi rend="caps">COLUMBIA, MISSOURI</hi>
                </fw>
                
                <opener>
                <dateline>12-29-57</dateline>
                
                
                <salute>Dear Slade Kendrick:</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>We haven't communicated often of late, but you are in my thoughts very often, and you are dear to me &#8212; one of the very dearest of friends. I just want to say hello, and bless your heart! <hi rend="underline">Bless both of you equally in that house of yours where I was happy!</hi> Mona and I share the feeling here expressed.</p>
                <closer>
                <salute>Yours always,</salute>
                <signed>John Neihardt</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
        
